            <div type="textpart" xml:id="Prescription">
               <label>Prescription</label>
               <ab>ለብሔረ፡ ሮሜ፡</ab>
               <ab>መልእክት፡ ቀዳማዊ፡ ኀበ፡ ሰብአ፡ ሮሜ፡</ab>
            </div>
            <div type="textpart" xml:id="Introduction">
               <label>Introduction</label>
            </div>
            <div type="textpart" xml:id="Epistle">
               <label>Epistle</label>
            </div>
            <div type="textpart" xml:id="Subscription">
               <label>Subscription</label>
               <ab>ተፈጸመ፡ በዝየ፡ ዘሮሜ፡</ab>
               <ab>ወተጽሕፈ፡ በቆሮንቶስ፡ ወተፈነወ፡ በእደ፡ ፌቤን፡ እንተ፡ ትትለአኮሙ፡ ለማኅበረ፡ ከንክራስ፡</ab>
            </div>
            <div type="textpart" xml:id="Stichometry">
               <label>Stichometry</label>
               <ab>ቃሉ፡ ፱፻ወ፶፡ ወምዕራፉ፡ ፲ወ፱፡ ለብሄረ፡ ሮሜ።</ab>
               <ab>ቃሉ፡ ፺ወ፩፡ ወምዕራፉ፡ ፲።</ab>
            </div>
